Class JobState.DatasetState

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WritableShim
    Enclosing class:
    JobState

    public static class JobState.DatasetState
extends JobState
    A subclass of JobState that is used to represent dataset states.

    A DatasetState does not contain any properties. Operations such as getProp(String) and setProp(String, Object) are not supported.
